### Create a new article
POST http://localhost:3000/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction Nodejs",
  "content": "This nodejs is a plataform to run javascript",
  "author": "john doe",
  "tags": ["node", "javascript"]
}

### List all articles
GET http://localhost:3000/articles

### Get a specific article by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/articles/8a9253d6-70ac-446a-a316-1e80e762f561

### Update an existing article by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/articles/8a9253d6-70ac-446a-a316-1e80e762f561
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction Nodejs update",
  "content": "This nodejs is a plataform to run javascript, update",
  "author": "john doe",
  "tags": ["node", "javascript", "update"]
}

### Delete article by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/articles/8a9253d6-70ac-446a-a316-1e80e762f561